This is the best of both worlds.
<br />

<br />
You get a BASIC version of the spell.
<br />

<br />
You can buy an upgrade from the merchant.
<br />

<br />
You can buy an even better upgrade from a player.
<br />

<br />
You can get an even better upgrade as a drop from a monster.
<br />

<br />
You can get an even better upgrade...
<br />

<br />
ect..
