				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Why would I buy appIII spells? 
<br />

<br />
Well, I make my own and it costs me a few silver, maybe 6 if prices are bad at the moment I'm buying my paper and quills (or bars/ornaments.) That's piddly. I can make 20sp off a 6sp investment anytime, not to mention doing wholesaler tasks -passively which is 12 silver a shot for what would be  an hour of gathering if I were silly enough to harvest exclusively. Paying in excess of 3gp for any non-master tier 2 spell or attack is IMO very silly at this stage of the game. 
<br />

<br />
If I weren't a scholar however, I'd... wait... that just wouldn't happen.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://home.comcast.net/~drdeathbane/images/scarecroweIV.gif" border="0" />
